/面试" target="_blank">面试</a>一般由导师举行，无需撰写<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/个人陈述" target="_blank">个人陈述</a>，但如撰写亦可用以参考*(4)(7)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23ucw1hiqnJIqwoP_MBHIqN9pMeFjkAK3UYXhH-0M3DazzObr9LWMNzgbi15IGnFnbtK03Fe1-q5oqChrd7GfS1ikuzahQwQW2UF2byeHzK4BFdhCWZQsF2O0QGdFZBVlvrPvNdF_QhvmOST1Wftg" target="_blank">Profile C</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVpDLZv0OpuQ3BAdeTwVHKXxfOIwO1oVhPGetE-NOVlzPrB0xuP9hFqhdw5QrBWSB0GiESQE-I7IDxu-HSm2-2beA6wkJoUYeeiwuCG0YegrrQ0Z7S7A5SaJ8N2ksEtNGy49kF" target="_blank">Entry requirements for postgraduate programmes China</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23qmkYo9iAHDcdTzbC3ULY0IiH3mV-VBfUc1CCZDXp5yLmKakdzpXB3teSelpnkY3sEw3tLyPwt0EaZdP3reSDb8r43yqQo-CmtY3sECtys3CaDNenQc1YoPc3ttwv3c9Q" target="_blank">MSc Management</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uKHpwOBAjWHgNljKoKhc6lPgx3J1gFCUHNDG15sSau0NbBH9MPLptIf0flhMfYmf0szJS6XtzMaWcRs3uFyPOjEBolFKMRmLlVnFYGmus_p4B9yGMQtkzF7-6AsB1fdv8R" target="_blank">PhD Management</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(5) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caiNkGpktwnn77777lunRtBLNxQSumGXGXAIEjWnSK7ikHX23sM2qZ0_ecNU6cEIU3j6TLJt_SD2tJDHEn9XoIDGW82iHl57KWt7pv-SfMwUoiBV49BhgOLB159f15oVPZd0MOd-GECcKEdcOMA3o26Tb" target="_blank">Pre-sessional courses Entry requirements</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(6) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibDKkgdlWQJ2ektaMMUq-oQBgFj3fDGFqY-AR_POY4TkTR1_di4vbhCzCiXvIFT_XO7GA3Gk3NnzjqOwy_qbIpA3iFRsEoZAvdAm6nQAu4Wi_XD7G_PGuCC4u7IuprYxHo7BpF2CC4u7Iues3AqoCFcQm" target="_blank">MSc Management Admissions statements</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(7) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Trq48pSDLZv0OPkFvvvvv0mj2L3YrbBXgsFIFIrQkFJ1DM6NbQJbxlZbAmE3QH5a8Ajutmzur5zpOWKl7BsH7NC5-Bt5_2nmnr95-XORqfq2Q_qWveSuQlP4v3txoX0loqViqDlBOtxIi7HcWO25z" target="_blank">PhD