生物化学</a>等）相关专业背景，二类A等荣誉学士学位或其同等水准以上。需要联系并指定导师，需要<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/面试" target="_blank">面试</a>，<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/面试" target="_blank">面试</a>一般由导师举行，需要撰写一份<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/个人陈述" target="_blank">个人陈述</a>。该项目受英国工程与自然科学研究委员会（EPSRC）和生物技术与生物科学研究委员会（BBSRC）资助，但其资金只提供给英国或欧盟学生，并无明确的<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金</a>提供给非欧盟国际学生*(3)(5)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=3rHk7m1TLNk2BiYgyYxyJTaPCmrCTJTqwGaxPqYph0ZvlcreLqFdiXxn6Lh0Al3WVnXh0ZupcKkraO2jf-1nGS-FTuBgm1rxnupR9fbhBZm1-f4ZSvZnPyhLEw-jSL_Q_UaO2qH15m2-ODD8wsCxaNn7L" target="_blank">Profile A</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Hr3vKzAMLwBRmQ7-ZZZZZnr8r4diE2LahlhlA9Ri31Cl0p6a3WcajPmauFDz6NWIX1Hs9rbqM_lR-_PXLiyW8blrBfP2VblUIfzQvXhNKExUo2hDSYJya2xyd" target="_blank">Entry requirements for postgraduate programmes China</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=0rRNYsU4kMv2wiK2xxxxxUT9B6sbzY8Bp6y6ytXGgNnqpNRZpsk0SIT-KLyAnIT7_tTAkt9XhLyXKeGqpWbOCIgA_7PR5HDFJZUlthmSD9TU3hM4v4O5XhyT3lI_RJ7IRJI5Aq97egWVQagyEa" target="_blank">Synthetic Biology (EPSRC and BBSRC Centre for Doctoral Training)</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ErbpefUfw5T1UNTugkXHChh4AylEtyYF3m70GvPod9zSxkyZ31kClHEvxbd9RkRAnAGd9SvWD21jOGOVEzwXuOxaIHIuMvf5iH5Z4Fszc4wxl_jtB1B8QAH5qzbvugei4Rf5h4yLCKnONS0CMcllOGhIKNhotfvFXxcp5" target="_blank">Pre-sessional courses Entry requirements</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(5) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=grPZ_xnAkawhoSnn77777l_RtBLNxQShMkMk9sKNj8whjvahfdEhMZLkmBsBxAf8LAnaLulU6ZlDTo2cT1_JLAhJiyG5xYhDMYnPiZCkC3-_OZXoC3wWo3woR1aoOtwrvelL9Ab-ZAQTNu" target="_blank">Synthetic Biology (Centre for Doctoral Training) Admissions statements</a> University of Bristol</p><h3>化学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:13.98%