，需要撰写一份<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/个人陈述" target="_blank">个人陈述</a>。该项目受威康信托（Welcom Trust）、英国生物技术与生物科学研究委员会（BBSRC）等资助，尽管非欧盟国际学生以自费为主，但仍可能有非常有限的<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金</a>向其提供*(3)(5)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=qrTydPt8wiWP5BOWqK34-BdcRvG1hNSfHuEBJuJGhic_M6VFLfIWgXpPIvFQt7vOdgdFQJvd_31DdYTCltbbOfW0XweV7dFbmein8OQhtcbuK4gZzJ47lwPggF8oK2nd1pdYTA9hg3RfjNjmt5hZhCbq-" target="_blank">Profile B</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUw0XLCZnSfulffffftonoGiaPSTBOROR-38au4dRchqBuwLBvN2B74HRcN-yuwineCBZWphVWAB236IOMp87PAjyMpTtPetU3phDE_Xo36IOKgLoEg0" target="_blank">Entry requirements for postgraduate programmes China</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVpMLwBRm64m99999DCD1JbA-H9dzMtotoYBInmGpJ2GxrbJpv-JbTMn9Ih4207ogMF_VMZhR_faL-vOzQjAbwponDUcYSyUHuGAKwgru4kOMY-bR3v2az_nOz" target="_blank">Biochemistry</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVdSk-uzkA4PqqqjXXvjPEFNWhpJZq7q7dbtWnSK7ikHZnQfZlA2ZUAajUTLWULC7Uyho8K5PzyDh1rZ3ayvN1rvwXt4EXrZEiFDR-FUadFZxgrDxftDx9cvwRt4wXr4xirVxSyHtmzio3" target="_blank">Pre-sessional courses Entry requirements</a> University of Bristol</p><p>(5) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Erbpef5RkUBr19jJlF6XsHYuFjN0XZvYmT_KihClYg8uTpdkzPWDf_73XePZhyK7C-zCBkAmZEnPCMCA9WDBVCBkXzjae0PjUXSMC-13OgmKv7xAPG9CRhk0rUpEylA5z_UhUSfz1zRmLfxkDTYe_YNG" target="_blank">Biochemistry Admissions statements</a> University of Bristol</p><h3>细胞与分子医学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:13.98%">			<p>QS世界排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:12.06%">			<p>8(49)</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.06%">			<p>学费/年</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.2%">			<p>￡17,500-￡29,700</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.08%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.62%">			<p><a href="http